From 1a8f63af6e72ee4e79e20d65c7565858a163868d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Wed, 22 Apr 2026 13:53:27 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add TUNING knobs, expand procedural and ingredients

- Tunable authored/procedural mix per slot (TUNING.authored_ratio)
- Tunable event influence on dish weighting (TUNING.event_weight_mult)
- 13 new procedural templates (pies, gratins, salads, fritters, tarts, etc.)
- 97 new ingredients spanning South/East Asian, Middle Eastern, African,
  pre-Columbian, steppe, northern foraging, and highland traditions
- Randomize and Reset buttons in the control panel
- Updated DESIGN.md with tuning knob documentation
---
